README_FUBRAD
=============

Possible spectral resolutions of FUBRAD.

Official FUBRAD resolutions:
----------------------------
nbands =  55  => sr % type = 'STR',      nchap =  6
nbands = 106  => sr % type = 'STR',      nchap = 57
nbands =  81  => sr % type = 'STR-HR22', nchap = 14

Test resolutions (inofficial)
-----------------------------
nbands =  55  => sr % type = 'ZHU',      nchap =  6
nbands = 106  => sr % type = 'ZHU',      nchap = 57
nbands = 146  => sr % type = 'STR-FLX',  nchap = 57
nbands = 146  => sr % type = 'STR-HR44', nchap = 57
nbands = 124  => sr % type = 'STR-HR22', nchap = 57
nbands = 144  => sr % type = 'KM',       nchap = 57
nbands = 143  => sr % type = 'KCK',      nchap = 57

Switch:
sr % type = 'STR-FLX'    ! hr from flux profile (25 SRC, 19 SRB)
sr % type = 'STR-HR44'   ! hr directly          (25 SRC, 19 SRB)
sr % type = 'STR-HR22'   ! hr directly          ( 3 SRC, 19 SRB)
sr % type = 'STR'        ! hr directly          ( 3 SRC,  1 SRB)
sr % type = 'KCK'        ! hr from flux profile (25 SRC, 16 SRB) 
sr % type = 'KM'         ! hr from flux profile (25 SRC, 17 SRB) 
sr % type = 'ZHU'        ! hr directly          ( 3 SRC,  1 SRB)
